      "raw_text": "Freight service for less than car\nload lots was installed by the Spo-\nkane & Inland road today between\nSpokane and stations on the Wav-\nerly branch. A stretch of \"a miles\nof territory tributary to Spokane is\nthus thrown open to small ship\npers. Coming into Spokane the\nfreight will leave Waverly at 10\na. m. and reach this city at $3.50.\nOutbound freight will leave here\nat 2 p. m.\n\n\nThe company yesterday received\ntwo Of the six 400 horsepower\nfreight motors ordered for the\nWaverly service. Each motor will\npull two freight cars. Six fine new\npassenger coaches were also de-\nlivered to the Spokane & Inland\nyesterday. Each will seat So pas\nsengers."
    }
